<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/1a75773af0854d99b57e17c3d6c8756d.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">《吉年吉祥》/李志向</span></img></p>
